Package: grml-live-addons
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: grml-live
Conflicts: grml-live (<< 0.9.13)
Description: templates/boot/addons for grml-live
 This package provides the boot addons known as the features
 providing bootoptions bsd, dos, and grub. You can safely
 skip this package if you don't need the addons.

Package: grml-live-compat
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: grml-live, grml-live-addons
Conflicts: grml-live-addons (<< 0.15.1~)
Description: templates/boot/addons unstable binaries for grml-live
 This package provides files from unstable, to allow building
 GRML on stable, and having all the boot templates actually work.

